<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Payment Failed - AWARI</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2c5aa0;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .error-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            color: #dc3545;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .payment-title {
            color: #2c5aa0;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .payment-details {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding: 5px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #666;
        }
        .detail-value {
            color: #333;
        }
        .amount {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #dc3545;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #2c5aa0;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #1e3d6f;
        }
        .retry-info {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .troubleshooting {
            background-color: #f8d7da;
            border: 1px solid #f5c6cb;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">AWARI</div>
            <div class="error-icon">✗</div>
            <h1 class="payment-title">Payment Failed</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hi <strong><%= user.firstName %></strong>,</p>
            
            <p>We're writing to inform you that your payment could not be processed successfully.</p>
            
            <div class="payment-details">
                <h3>Payment Details</h3>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Amount:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value amount">₦<%= payment?.amount || '0.00' %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Payment Method:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value"><%= payment?.method || 'Card' %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Transaction ID:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">#<%= payment?.id?.slice(-8) || 'N/A' %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Date:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value"><%= new Date().toLocaleDateString() %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Status:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value" style="color: #dc3545; font-weight: bold;">Failed</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="retry-info">
                <h4>What You Can Do:</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Try using a different payment method</li>
                    <li>Check that your card details are correct</li>
                    <li>Ensure you have sufficient funds in your account</li>
                    <li>Contact your bank if the issue persists</li>
                    <li>Retry the payment from your dashboard</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="troubleshooting">
                <h4>Common Reasons for Payment Failure:</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Insufficient funds in your account</li>
                    <li>Incorrect card details (number, expiry date, CVV)</li>
                    <li>Card has expired or been blocked</li>
                    <li>Bank security restrictions</li>
                    <li>Network connectivity issues</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <p>Don't worry! Your booking is still reserved for a limited time. Please try again or contact our support team if you need assistance.</p>
            
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="<%= actionUrl || 'https://awari.com/dashboard' %>" class="cta-button">
                    <%= actionText || 'Retry Payment' %>
                </a>
            </div>
            
            <p>If you continue to experience issues or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
            
            <p>Best regards,<br>The AWARI Team</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This email was sent to <%= user.email %> regarding your payment attempt.</p>
            <p>&copy; 2024 AWARI. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
